race.comment: BONNIE DIVA (2) ran below best last time finishing sixth (20.71) over 342m at this track from Box 7. Has a solid record from this box including two wins and a minor placing. Key runner on her best form. ARCHER NINE (1) is boxed nicely on the inside. Last start finished 4th in a Grade 4/5 on November 9 over 375m at Broken Hill behind Del Mar Jessie beaten 10 lengths (22.42). Suited here and expected to run well. SHAKA GOES BANG (7) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing sixth (20.67) last time in a Other at this track. Form at the trip sound including 11 wins. Has the ability to give this a shake. NO SUGAR THANKS (5) has top-three aspirations after placing last time.
